# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞/名詞)  
<explanation>  
yue:喺賭博、投資或者生意當中，當虧損到某程度，就停止繼續投入，避免損失再擴大（量詞：次、場）  
eng:to stop losses; to cut one's losses  
<eg>  
yue:呢次股市大跌，佢哋即刻止蝕，唔再追加資金。 (nei1 ci3 guk1 si4 daai1 daai3, keoi1 dei6 zik1 zih2 jat1, m4 ngoi4 zau1 gaa1 zaam1.)  
eng:When the stock market crashed this time, they immediately cut their losses and stopped adding more capital. [end of text]


